{"name":"John Jr.","size":"medium","type":"fiend","tag":"shapechanger","alignment":"chaotic lawful","hitDice":"5","armorName":"none","shieldBonus":2,"natArmorBonus":8,"otherArmorDesc":"14","speed":"30","burrowSpeed":"0","climbSpeed":"0","flySpeed":"0","hover":false,"swimSpeed":"0","customHP":true,"customSpeed":false,"hpText":"29","speedDesc":"30 ft.","strPoints":"13","dexPoints":"12","conPoints":"14","intPoints":"12","wisPoints":"16","chaPoints":"9","blindsight":"0","blind":false,"darkvision":"60","tremorsense":"0","truesight":"0","telepathy":0,"cr":"4","customCr":"3 (700 XP)","customProf":2,"isLegendary":false,"legendariesDescription":"The doppelganger can take 3 legendary actions, choosing from the options below. Only one legendary action option can be used at a time and only at the end of another creature's turn. The doppelganger regains spent legendary actions at the start of its turn.","isLair":false,"lairDescription":"When fighting inside its lair, the doppelganger can invoke the ambient magic to take lair actions. On initiative count 20 (losing initiative ties), the doppelganger can take one lair action to cause one of the following effects:","lairDescriptionEnd":"The doppelganger can't repeat an effect until they have all been used, and it can't use the same effect two rounds in a row.","isMythic":false,"mythicDescription":"If the doppelganger's mythic trait is active, it can use the options below as legendary actions for 1 hour after using {Some Ability}.","isRegional":false,"regionalDescription":"The region containing the doppelganger's lair is warped by the creature's presence, which creates one or more of the following effects:","regionalDescriptionEnd":"If the doppelganger dies, the first two effects fade over the course of 3d10 days.","properties":[],"abilities":[{"name":"Shapechanger","desc":"[MON] can use his action to polymorph into a Small or Medium humanoid he has seen, or back into its true form. His statistics, other than his size, are the same in each form. Any equipment [MON] is wearing or carrying isn't transformed. He reverts to its _true form_ if he dies."},{"name":"Flesh recollection","desc":"As part of _Shapechanging_ into a target [MON] can access some of their subconscious memories (at the DM's discretion)."},{"name":"Sunlight Sensitivity","desc":"While in sunlight, [MON] has disadvantage on attack rolls, as well as on Wisdom (Perception) checks that rely on sight."},{"name":"Ambusher","desc":"[MON] has advantage on attack rolls against any creature it has surprised."},{"name":"Surprise Attack","desc":"If [MON] surprises a creature and hits it with an attack during the first round of combat, the target takes an extra [3d6] damage from the attack."},{"name":"Shelter the Faithful","desc":"Someone gave [MON] this vial, maybe they know more about what went wrong."}],"actions":[{"name":"Warhammer","desc":"_Melee Weapon Attack:_ [STR ATK] to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. _Hit:_ [STR 1D8] bludgeoning damage (versatile 1d10)."},{"name":"Light Crossbow","desc":"_Ranged Weapon Attack:_ [DEX ATK] to hit, range 80/320 ft., one target. _Hit:_ [DEX 1D8] piercing damage."},{"name":"Cantrips","desc":"[MON] knows and can cast _Thaumaturgy_, _Guidance_, and _Spare the Dying_"},{"name":"Beseech the Outer God","desc":"[MON] may call upon power from an enigmatic and malevolent source to perform feats of magic (at the DM's discretion). However, using this power, especially multiple times per day, is damaging to the soul and exhausting to the body."}],"bonusActions":[],"reactions":[],"legendaries":[],"mythics":[],"lairs":[],"regionals":[],"sthrows":[{"name":"con","order":2},{"name":"cha","order":5}],"skills":[{"name":"deception","stat":"cha","note":" (ex)"},{"name":"medicine","stat":"wis"},{"name":"perception","stat":"wis"},{"name":"survival","stat":"wis"}],"damagetypes":[],"specialdamage":[],"conditions":[{"name":"charmed"}],"languages":[{"name":"Abyssal","speaks":true},{"name":"Common","speaks":true},{"name":"Undercommon","speaks":true}],"understandsBut":"","shortName":"John","pluralName":"","doubleColumns":true,"separationPoint":2,"damage":[]}